'''Juneteenth''', ofisialmente '''Juneteenth National Independence Day''' i tambe konosí komo '''Jubilee Day''',<ref>{{en}}{{citeer web|datum=1975-06-12|title=Cel-Liberation Style! Fourth Annual Juneteenth Day Kicks off June 19. |werk=Milwaukee Star |url=http://www.infoweb.newsbank.com/apps/readex/doc?p=EANX&docref=image/v2%3A12A7AE31A7B3CA6B%40EANX-12BA74AAA9B9AFB8%402442576-12BA74AAB9BFAD18%401-12BA74ABAE646B48%40Cel-Liberation%2BStyle%2521%2BFourth%2BAnnual%2BJuneteenth%2BDay%2BKicks%2Boff%2BJune%2B19 |bezochtdatum=2022-06-15}}</ref> '''Emancipation Day''',<ref>{{en}}{{Citeer web|first=Daniella|last=Silva|title=What to know about Juneteenth, the emancipation holiday|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/what-know-about-juneteenth-emancipation-holiday-n1231179|datum=2020-06-16|bezochtdatum=2022-06-15|uitgever=NBC News}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{citeer web |first=Kenneth C.|last=Davis|url=https://www.smithsonianmag.com/history/juneteenth-our-other-independence-day-16340952/ |title=Juneteenth: Our Other Independence Day |werk=Smithsonian Magazine|datum=2011-06-15|bezochtdatum=2022-06-15}}</ref> '''Freedom Day''', i '''Black Independence Day''', ta un dia di fiesta nashonal na [[Estadonan Uni di Merka]] pa konmemorá e emansipashon di [[Afro-Merikano|afro-merikanonan]] [[Sklabitut|sklavisá]]. Komunmente ta opservá e dia aki tambe pa selebrá e kultura afro-merikano. Juneteenth a originá na [[Galveston]], [[Teksas]] i desde 1865 a wòrdu selebrá tur aña riba dia [[19 di yüni]] na varios lugá ront Merka.

[[File:General order No. 3 of June 19, 1865.jpg|thumb|240px|Dekreto General no. 3, [[19 di yüni]] [[1865]]]]
E konmemorashon di Juneteenth, un akrónimo di ''June'' (yüni) i ''nineteenth'' (diesnuebe) ta tuma lugá riba e aniversario di 19 di yüni 1865, fecha di Dekreto General no.3 di general Gordon Granger, proklamando libertat pa e personanan sklabisá na Teksas, e ultimo estado di e Konfederashon di estadonan merikano ku sklabitut institutionalisá.<ref name="gates">{{en}}{{citeer web|last=Gates Jr.|first=Henry Louis|datum=2013-01-16|titel=What Is Juneteenth?|url=https://www.pbs.org/wnet/african-americans-many-rivers-to-cross/history/what-is-juneteenth/|publisher=PBS|bezochtdatum=2022-06-15}}</ref> Dia 17 di yüni 2021 Juneteenth a keda rekonosí komo dia di fiesta nashonal despues ku presidente [[Joe Biden]] a pone su firma bou e lei di "Juneteenth National Independence Day Act".<ref>{{en}}{{Citeer web|last=Cathey|first=Libby|datum=2021-06-17|title=Biden signs bill making Juneteenth, marking the end of slavery, a federal holiday|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/biden-sign-bill-making-juneteenth-federal-holiday-commemorating/story?id=78335485|uitgever=ABC News|bezochtdatum=2022-06-15}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Citeer web  |date=2021-06-17|title=Biden signs bill making Juneteenth, marking the end of slavery, a federal holiday |url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/speeches-remarks/2021/06/17/remarks-by-president-biden-at-signing-of-the-juneteenth-national-independence-day-act/ |bezochtdatum=2022-06-15|werk=whitehouse.gov}}</ref>

